    "The results of the rescaling for a single image are shown in Fig. 4b.",
    "Note that using this method, values outside the [0, 1] range are expected.",
    "Thereby, the downscaled image is processed and any output value exceeding such range is truncated to 0 or 1.",
    "The rescaled images are then reshaped back to the n 2 ×1 column vector representation format and stored in a new matrix.",
    "Now this image can be used as input in the crossbar array of memristors."
